    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase the Ticket Queue and how to use it, including:</p><ul><li><p>How to filter\u00a0the view: ticket number, customer, device, etc.</p></li><li><p>How to sort the view by column</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mqORS8DMTy4\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mqORS8DMTy4</a><h2 id=\"NavigatingtheTicketQueue(video)-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932754986/List+Views\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932754986\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">List Views Overview</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932525644/List+Filters\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932525644\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">List Filters</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932656694/Saving+and+Sharing+Custom+List+Views\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932656694\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Saving and Sharing Custom List Views</a></p>",
